==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
A [[mnemonic]] device to aid with [[abacus]] addition of numbers greater than five.

Literally: Three, down five, take away two.

Ex. 3+3=6
<ol>
<li>Start with three beads on the bottom (each lower bead is equal to 1).
<li>Move one of the top beads down (each top bead is equal to 5).
<li>Take away two of the beads from the bottom.
<li>This leaves you with one top bead (5) and one bottom bead (1), for a total of 6.
</ol>
